quran[111]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,"Alif, laam, Raa, ∆äeen ko Aayeeje deftere …ďanngunde nden. fee√Īnde."
  12,2,"Minen min njippiniriinde janngeteende [e …óemngal] Aarabu, mbelejo'o, on kaqqilay."
  12,3,"Minen Mi…óen pillano maa ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e fillayee, e …óuu ko min mbahyi e maa…óa ndee Alqur'aanaare, hay si woniino ado mayre, ko a jeyaa…óo e welsindii…ďe …ďen.b"
  12,4,"Tuma nde Yuusufu maakannoo baabamakko: ""eehey may baaba', mi yi'ii [e koy…óol] koode sappo e go'o, naange ngen kadi e lewru ndun; mi yi'ii …óin no cujjana kam""."
  12,5,"[Baaba makko] maaki: ""Eehey ma …ďinngel am, wota a fillano musi…ó…ďe maa …ďen koy…óol maa ngol sakko …ďe fewjane feere; pellet seytaane ko ga√Īo aade …ďanngu…óo(.pee√Ī…óo.)"
  12,6,"Ko wano nii Joomi maa su…ďoray maa, O anndinma firo koy…ói, o timmina dokke makko on e maa…óa e …ďeynguure Yaaquuba nden, wano o timminirnoo mo e baabiraa…ďe maa …ďen …ói…óo: Ibraahiima e ishaaqa. Pellet Joomi maa ko ganndu…óo √Ďee√Ī…óo."
  12,7,"GooŇč…óii wonii e Yuusufa e musi…ó…ďe makko …ďeen, taskuyeeji wonan¬īde la…ďndotoo…ďe …ďen."
  12,8,"tuma nde …ďe mbi'noo: ""Pellet ko Yuusufa e neene-gooto(musi…ó…óo )mun on …ďuraa yi…óeede ka ben-men dii enen, enen le ko en jamaa …óuu…óu…ďe. Pellet baabamen wonii e majjere …ďanngunde""."
  12,9,"Mbaree Yuusufa maa fero…óon mo e leydi; yeeso baaba mon ngon heeranoo on, ngonton …ďaawo …óum yim…ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ďe""."
  12,10,"Gooto e ma…ď…ďe wi'i: ""Wota on mbarYuusufa, mbeddee mo ka ni…ďe woyndu yoga e setee…ďe hoccay mo, si on laatike golloo…ďe""."
  12,11,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""eeheyma baaba amen, ko he…ďu-maa a hoolotaako amen e fii Yuusufa? Minen le ko men laa…ďam…ďe mo reedu""."
  12,12,"Accitid-mo e amen o √Īaama, o fija,minen ko men reenoo…ďe mo."
  12,13,"O maaki: ""miin no suninat kam nde njahdoton e makko; mi…óo huli nde boyeeru ndu √Īaamata-mo tawa Ko on mbelsindi-…óoon e makko""."
  12,14,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Pellet si saafaandu √Īaamii mo e hoore ko men jamaa …óuu…óu…ďe, haray ko men hayru…ďe""(pertu…ďe.)"
  12,15,"Nde …ďe njahdunoo e makko, …ďe fottani ukkugol mo ka ni…ďe woyndu, min mbahayini e makko: ""Ma a haaltayan …ďe …óee kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe hara …ďe so'aa anndude"".…ďe( tinaani).."
  12,16,"∆Āe ngrti ka baaba ma…ď…ďe kiikii…óe he…ďe woya ."
  12,17,"∆Āe mb'i: ""Ko an yo baaben amen, minen men njehii mi…óen adondira, men ngacci Yuusufa ka kaake amen saafaandu ndun √Īaami mo. A hoolotaako min non, hay si min ngonii gooŇč…óu…ďe""."
  12,18,"∆Āe ngardi e dolokke makko on hino moddi ∆īii∆īam fenaande. o maaki: ""si ko woni, woŇčkiiji mon …óin cu…óinanii on fiyaaku. Ko mu√Īal mo∆ī∆īal [heddanii kam]! Ko Alla woni ballitor…óo e ko sifoto…óon kon""."
  12,19,"Setee…ďe ngari, …ďe nuli ∆īoogoowo ma…ď…ďe on, o jippini baagal makko ngal. O wi'i: ""Ee wel¬®-welo am! E hino paykum!"" ∆Āe cuu…óiri mo keyee ma…ď…ďe. Alla non ko ganndu…óo ko …ďe ngollata kon."
  12,20,"∆Āe njeeyiri mo coggel pam…óungel: dirhamo√Ī limotoo-ko√Ī. ∆Āe ngoni welsindii…ďe e fii makko."
  12,21,"Coot…óo mo on Misra wi'ani …ďeyngu makko: ""Teddin jipporde makko. Hino gasa ka o nafa en maa njogito…óen mo …ďi…ó…óo"". Ko nii min ko…óniri Yuusufa ka leydi fii yo minn nganndin mo firo koy…ói. Alla ko poolu…óo e fiyaaku makko on: kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen nganndaa."
  12,22,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaagu makko, min ngokki mo faamu e ganndal. Ko wano nii min njo…ďirta mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  12,23,"OOn [debbo] mo on woni e suudu mun …óa…ď…ďiri mo hoore-makko. O soki baafe …óen o wi'i: ""mi heblanii-mo-ma!"" o maaki: ""Moolaare Alla! Jey…óo kam on mo∆ī∆īinii weerde am. Si ko woni, too√Īoo…ďe …ďen maletaake""."
  12,24,"GooŇč…óii [debbo] on himmanii oon. KaŇčko kadi o himmanayno mo si wanaa o yi'ii hujja Joomi makko on. Ko nii [min gerdiri] fii yo min njiiltu mo e bone e paŇčkare. Pellet ko o jeyaa…óo e jeyaa…ďe amen la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďeen."
  12,25,"∆Āe …ói…óo kala …ďe ngidondiri ka baafal, o seekiri dolokke oya oon …ďaawo. ∆Āe tawi moodi makko ka baafal. [debbo] on wi'i: ""Ko hol…óum woni njo…ďdi on paalanaa…óo …ďeynguure maa nden bonki si wanaa yo soke [o leptiree] lepte muus…óe?"""
  12,26,"[Yuusufu] maaki: ""Ko kaŇčko …óa…ď…ďiri kam hoore-am"". Tawanoo…óo e yim…ďe [debbo] on ceeditii: ""Si tawii dolokke mum on ko yeeso seekiraa, haray ko [debbo] oon gooŇč…ói, kaŇčko [gorko] on ko jeyaa…óo e fen…ďe …ďeen."
  12,27,"Si tawii noon dolokke makko oon ka …ďaawo seekiraa, haray [debbo] on fenii, kaŇčko [gorko] on ko o jeyaa…óo gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen."
  12,28,"Nde [moodi makko] yi'noo dolokke oon ko …ďaawo seekori, o wi'i: ""∆äum ko jeyaa…óum e pewje mon! Pellet pewje mon …óen ko maw…óe!""."
  12,29,"Yuusufa, …óuurno gah e …óum. Aan [debbo on], imsinano junuubi(bakkaat) maa …óin; tawde pellet a jeyaama e woop…ďe …ďeen""."
  12,30,"Rew…ďe …ďen ka saare mbi'i: ""Debbo laam…óo on …óa…ď…ďirii kurka makko o hoore-makko! GooŇč…óii yi…óde …ďurtirii mo. Minen dey mi…óen nji'a oo [debbo] e majjere …ďanngunde""."
  12,31,"Nde o nannoo pewje ma…ď…ďe …óen, o nulani …ďe, o hebilani …ďe ngawluuji, o jonni gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe la…ďi, o wi'i: ""Yaltu e ma…ď…ďe!"". Nde …ďe nji'unoo mo, …ďe mawnini mo, …ďe ta∆īi juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe mbi'i: ""Kaawee Alla! Oo wanaa …ďanndiŇčke, oo wonaani si wanaa malayiko teddu…óo""."
  12,32,"O wi'i: ""Ko oo mo'on felir…óon kamm fii mun, gooŇč…óii mi …óa…ď…ďirii mo hoore-makko o ha…óitii. Si wonii o wa…óaani ko mi yamirta mo kon, ma o soke ma o laato jeyaa…óo e hoy…ďe …ďen""."
  12,33,"O maaki: ""Joomi am, Ko kaso oon …ďurani kam e ko …ďe noddata kam e mun kon. Si a pottinaani kam pewje ma…ď…ďe …óen, mi oo√Īoto e ma…ď…ďe, mi jeyee e majju…ďe …ďe""."
  12,34,"Joomi makko jaabinani mo, O firliti e makko pewje ma…ď…ďe …óen. Pellet, ko KaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ganndu…óo O."
  12,35,"Refti fee√Īani (rew…ďe) …ďen …ďaawo nde …ďe nji'i maandeeji …óin, ma …ďe cok-mbo tigi haa e saaji."
  12,36,"Sukaa…ďe …ói…óo naatidi e makko ka kaso. Go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe wi'i: ""Min mi hoy…óii hoore-am mi…óo siiwa sanngara"". Oya kadi wi': ""Min mi hoy…óii hoore-am mi…óo ronndii ka hoore-am cobbal, colli no √Īaama e maggal"". Humpitii min firo …óin, minen men nji'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  12,37,"O maaki: ""√Ďaametee mo wona…óon okkoreede on aratah on si wanaa mi humpitay on firo mun ado o arde on. ∆äuum mo'on ko jeyee…óum e ko Joomi am anndini lam. Min mi …óalii diina yim…ďe …ďe ngooŇč…óinaa Alla, hara kam…ďe e fii laakara ko …ďe yeddu…ďe""."
  12,38,"Njookku-mi diina baabiraa…ďe am …ďen: Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba. Haananaa men nde men kafidata e Alla hay e huunde. ∆äuum ko jeyaa…óum e …ďural Alla e dow amen e hoore yim…ďe …ďeen; kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe njettataa."
  12,39,"Eehey mon won¬īdii…ďe am …ói…óo ka kaso! E ko dewetee…ói ceertu…ói …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, kaa ko Alla Gooto pool…óo o?"
  12,40,"On ndewani gah mum, si wonah in…óe …óe innu…óon …óum, onon e baabiraa…ďe mon, Alla jippinanaani …óen hujja. √Ďaawoore ndeen alanah si wanaa Alla. O yamirii wota on ndw si wanaa KaŇčko. Ko …óuum woni diina √Īii…ďuka kan; kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe nganndaa."
  12,41,"Eehey mon won¬īdii…ďe am …ói…óo ka kaso! Go…ó…óo e mo'on yarnay koohoo mun on sanngara; oya on, o fetee, colli …óin √Īaama ka hoore makko. Fiyaaku mo la…ďndi…óon fii mun on √Īaawaama."
  12,42,"O maakani on mo o sikke da…óay e ma…ď…ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo: ""JaŇčto lam ka koohoojo maa on"". Seytaane yejjintini mo jaŇčtanagol koohoojo makko on. [Yuusufu] √Īii…ďiti ka kaso yoga e duu…ďi."
  12,43,"Laam…óo on wi'i: ""Min mi yi'ii (e koy…óol) na'i jee…ói…ói pay…ói, na √Īaama poo∆īu…ói jee…ói…ói …óin, e butaali jee…ói…ói kecci, e go…ó…ói goo joor…ói. Eheymon dental, pirtanee kam ngol koy…óol am, si on laatike firtoo…ďe koy…ói""."
  12,44,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Ko jii…ďu-jaa…ďu koy…ói ! min ngonaani anndu…ďe firo koy…ói !""."
  12,45,"Da…ónoo…óo on e …ďeya …ói…óo miijitii …ďaawo dumunna o wi'i: ""Min mi humpitay on firo maggol. Nulee kam""."
  12,46,"Yuusufu, an yo gooŇč…óu…óo! haalani min fii na'i jee…ói…ói pay…ói, na √Īaama poo∆īu…ói jee…ói…ói …óin, e butaali jee…ói…ói kecci e go…ó…ói jooru…ói, mbelejo'o mi ruttoo ka yim…ďe …ďen, belejo'o, …ďe ngannday""."
  12,47,"O maaki: ""On ndemat duu…ói jee…ói…ói jokkondir…ói. Kala ko co√Ī…óon, ngccon …óum ka dukkal(butaali) mun, si wanaa see…óa e kon ko √Īaamoton""."
  12,48,"Refti aroyat …ďaawo …óum, duu…ďi jee…ói…ói ca…ótu…ói, …óin (duu…ďi) no √Īaama …óuum ko marna…óon …ói si wonaa see…óa e ko maroton [fii awdi]."
  12,49,"Refti aroya …ďaawo …óuum, hitaande, ko e mayre yim…ďe …ďen to…ďetee, ko e mayre kadi …ďe kamata."
  12,50,"Laam…óo on wi'i: ""ngaddanee kam on"". Nde imminaa…óo on arunoo mo, o maaki: ""Rutto ka koohoojo maa on la…ďndo…óaa mo: Ko woni fiyaaku …ďen rew…ďe ta∆īnoo…ďe juu…óe mun …óen? Pellet Joomi am ko ganndu…óo pewje ma…ď…ďe …óen""."
  12,51,"[Laam…óo on] wi'i: ""Ko hol…óum wonnoo fiyaaku mon tuma …óa…ď…ďirno…óon Yuusufa hoore-makko?"" ∆Āe mbi'i: ""Moolaare Alla! min nganndiraa mo ko boni"". ∆Āeyngu laam…óo on wi'i: ""Jooni goonga kan fee√Īii. Ko min …óa…ď…ďirnoo mo hoore-makko, pellet ko o jeyaa…óo e gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen""."
  12,52,"""∆äuum ko fii yo o anndu won¬īde mi jamfaaki mo ka wirnii, e won¬īde Alla fewnatah pewje jamfotoo…ďe …ďen."
  12,53,"Mi la…ď…ďinaa hoore-am, tawde woŇčkii ko heewkii yamirde bone, si wanah kiin ki Joomi am yurmini. Joomi am ko jaafotoo…óo jurmotoo…óo."
  12,54,"Laam…óo on wi'i: ""ngaddanee kam mo, mi heertinana mo hoore-am"". Nde o yewtunoo mo, o wi'i: ""Aa on hannde ka amen, ko a jom-nokku koolaa…óo""."
  12,55,"O maaki: ""Wa…óam e hoore-ngaluuji leydi ndin: ko mi deenoowo ganndu…óo""."
  12,56,"Ko wano nii min √Īimnirani Yuusufa ka leydi, homo jippora e mayri nokku ka o yi…ói. mi…óen ke…ďnira yurmeende amen nden on mo min muuyi, min njeebataaka njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen."
  12,57,"Pellet ko njo…ďdi laakara ndiin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe laatii gooŇč…óu…ďe."
  12,58,"-Musi…ó…ďe-baaba-gootoo…ďe Yuusufa …ďeen ngari …ďe naati ka makko. O annditi …ďe, kono kam…ďe …ďe paayti mo."
  12,59,"Tuma nde o hebllannoo…ďe doŇčlle ma…ď…ďe …óeen, o maaki: ""ngaddanee kam musi…ó…óo mon baaba-gooto. E on nji'aani mi…óo timmina …ďetu ngun, e won¬īde ko mi …ďurdo mo∆ī∆īude e weernoo…ďe …ďen?""(jippinoo…ďr)."
  12,60,"Si on ngaddanaani kam mo, haray …ďetu alanaa on ka am …óoo; wota on …ďado kamm kadi""."
  12,61,"∆Āe mb'i: ""min …óa…ď…ďiray mo baba makko, minen ko men golloo…ďe (…óuum)""."
  12,62,"O maakani golloo…ďe makko …ďen: ""mba…óee coggeeji(njigguuji) ma…ď…ďe …óin ka doŇčle ma…ď…ďe: belejo'o …ďe ngannditat …ói si …ďe nduttima ka yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, belejo'o …ďe njiiltoto""."
  12,63,"Tuma nde …ďe nduuttinoo ka ben ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbi'i: ""eeheyma ben(baaba) amen, min ska…óaama …ďetu. neldu amen musi…ó…óo amen on, men …ďetanee. Ko men reenoo…ďe mo""."
  12,64,"O maaki: ""Hara mi hooloray on e fii makko, si wonaa no mi hoolornoo on non e musi…ó…óo-neene-gooto makko on ko adii? Ko Alla woni mo∆ī∆īo deenoowo, ko KaŇčko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude yurmotoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  12,65,"Nde …ďe ngudditunoo doŇčle ma…ď…ďe …óeen, …ďe tawi cogguuji(njigguuji) ma…ď…ďe …óin ruttaama e ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe mbi'i: ""eeyma yo ben amen, ko men …óa…ď…ďata [kadi]? ∆äii ko cogguuji amen, …ói nduttaama e amen. Mi…óen njiggana yim…ďe amen, men ndeena musi…ó…óo amen on, men …ďeydora …ďetu ngelooba; …óuum ko …ďetu newiingu""."
  12,66,"O maaki: ""Mi immindintaa(neldatah) mo e moo…óon haa ∆īettanon mi ahadi ka Alla, won¬īde on ngrtiranat kam mo si wonaa hara on ku…ďinda"". ∆Āaawo …ďe ∆īettanii mo ahadi ma…ď…ďe ndin, o maaki: ""Alla e dow ko wowlu…óen kon, ko o deenoowo""."
  12,67,"O maaki: ""eeheymin …ďi…ó…ďe am, wota on naatiroy e damal gootal, naatiree e dame ceertu…óe. Mi dun-cantaa on e (muy…óe) Alla hay e huunde. √Ďaawoore alanaa si wonaa Alla: Ko e makko mi fawii, ko e makko kadi, yo fawo fawotoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  12,68,"Nde …ďe naatirnoo nokku ka baaba ma…ď…ďe yamirnoo …ďe …óon, …óum wonaano no duncana …ďe [ko iwri] ka Alla si wanaa haaju wonunoo…óo e fittaandu Yaaquuba mo o gasini. KaŇčko on, ko o jom-ganndal ngal min anndini mo. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe nganndaa."
  12,69,"Nde …ďe naatnoo ka Yuusufa, o ma…ď…ďi musi…ó…óo-neene-gooto makko on e makko, o maaki: ""Ko mi musi…ó…óo-neene-gooto maa, wata a sunor ko …ďe ngollatnoo""."
  12,70,"Tuma nde o hebilannoo …ďe doŇčle ma…ď…ďe …óen, o wa…ói …ďetirgal ngal ka doŇčngal musi…ó…óo-neene-gooto makko on, refti ewnotoo…óo eewnii: ""eeymon yo setee…ďe, Ko on wuy…ďe""."
  12,71,"∆Āe fewtiti e ma…ď…ďe …ďe mbi'i: ""Ko hol…óuum katti…óon?"""
  12,72,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""minn kattike …ďetirde laam…óo on. Hino woodani kala gaddu…óo ngal, doŇčngal ngelooba, ko miin woni pawtii…óo …óuum""."
  12,73,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""min ngoo…óndirii Alla, gooŇč…óii ho…óon nganndi min ngaraani bonnugol ka leydi, min laataaki kadi wuy…ďe""."
  12,74,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Ko wonata njo…ďdi makko si tawii ko on fenoo…ďe?"""
  12,75,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Njo…ďdi makko: ko kala mo: […óuum] tawaa ka doŇčngal mun, haray ko kaŇčko [tigir] woni njo…ďdi mun. Ko wano non min njo…ďitirta too√Īoo…ďe …ďen""."
  12,76,"[Yuusufu] fu…ó…óori doŇčle ma…ď…ďe …óen ado doŇčngalmusi…ó…óo- neene-gooto makko on; refti o yaltiniri nde ka doŇčngal musi…ó…óo-neene-gooto makko on. Ko wano non men fewjirani Yuusufa, [tawde] o hattantaano nanngude musi…ó…óo-neene-gooto makko on ka sariya laam…óo on, si wonaa hara ko Alla muuyi. Mi…óen …ďantana darajaaji on mo min muuyi. No e dow kala jom-ganndal ganndo [goo]."
  12,77,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Si o wujjii, haray mus…óo- neene-gooto makko wujjiino ko adii"". Yuusufu mari …óum ka woŇčkii makko, o fe√Ī√Īinanaani …ďe …óuum. o maaki: ""Ko onon …ďuri bon¬īde nokku! Ko Alla …ďuri anndude ko cifoto…óon""."
  12,78,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""heyma yo laam…óo on, oo no mari baabiraawo nawyu…óo oggos; ∆īettu gooto e amen lomto makko. Menen men nji'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  12,79,"O maaki: ""Moolaare Alla nde min nanngata si wanaa oon mo men tawi doŇčle amen …óeen e juu…óe mun. Mene haray ontuma ko men too√Ī…ďe""."
  12,80,"Nde …ďe ta∆īinoo fii hettugol mo, …ďe martiti ko …ďe gunndondir…ďe. Maw…óo ma…ď…ďe on wi'i: ""E on nganndaa won¬īde baaba mon ∆īettodii e mo'on ahadi ka Alla, e aranun tuma belsindino…óon e Yuusufa? Mi seerataa leydi ndin haa baaba am duŇčanoo kam maa o √Īaawana kam [hettugol mo], ko KaŇčko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e √Īaawoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  12,81,"Nduttee ka baaba mon mbi'on: ""eeheyma yo baaba amen, …ďi…ó…óo maa on wujjii. min ceedaaki si wonaa ko men nganndi, men wonaani reen…ďe ko wirnii."
  12,82,"La…ďndo (yim…ďe) saare nden nde men ngonunoo e mun, e setee…ďe …ďen …ďe men kawrondirnoo e mun. Pellet ko men gooŇč…óu…ďe""."
  12,83,"[Yaaquuba] maaki: ""WoŇčkiiji mon …óin cu…óanii on fiyaake! Ko mu√Īal labangal. Hino hasii ka Alla artiranta mi …ďe, …ďe denndaangal. Ko KaŇčko woni ganndu…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo""."
  12,84,"O …óuurnii …ďe o maaki: ""Ee suno am e fii Yuusufa!"" Gite makko …óen ndanwiri suno. Ko o cuu…ó…óo suno."
  12,85,"∆Āe mb'i: ""min ngoo…ódirii Alla! A seerataa ha…óa jaŇčtoo fii Yuusufa, haa ngonaa horsu…óo maa ngonaa jeyaa…óo e halkii…ďe …ďen""."
  12,86,"O maaki: ""nganndee ko e Alla mi wullitotoo ngannde am e sunaare am. Mi…óo anndi ka Alla ko on nganndaa""."
  12,87,"""Eeheymon …ďi…ó…ďe am, njehee tefon fii Yuusufa e musi…ó…óo neene-gooto makko on. Wota on ta∆īo e yurmeende Alla. Ko fii, ta∆īotaako e yurmeende Alla si wanaa yim…ďe yeddu…ďe …ďen""."
  12,88,"Nde …ďe naatunoo ka makko [kaŇčko Yuusufa], …ďe wi'i: ""Ko an yo laam…óo, lorra he…ďii men memen e …ďeynguure amen; men angadii e sil'a jaasu…óo. Hu…ďnan men …ďetu ngun, cakko-…óaa e amen. Pellet, Alla yo…ďay sakkotoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  12,89,"O maaki: ""Enee, on ngannditii ko mba…óuno…óon Yuusufa e musi…ó…óo neene-gooto makko on kon tuma nde ngonno…óon majju…ďe?"""
  12,90,"∆Āe mbii'i: ""Kere ko aan woni Yuusufa?"" O maaki: ""Ko miin woni Yuusufa. Oo …óoo ko mi√Īam. GooŇč…óii Alla mo∆ī∆īike e amen. Ko fii, mo gom…óii o mu√Ī√Īike, pellet, Alla yeebataa njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen""."
  12,91,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""min ngoo…óndiri Alla, Alla …ďurnii ma e amen, men woniino woop…ďe""."
  12,92,"O maaki: ""Feloore alaa e hoore-mon hannde! Yo Alla yawtan on. Ko Kano woni …ďur…óo Yurmotoo…ďe""."
  12,93,"Njehhdee e oo dolokke am …óoo, mberlo…óon mo ka yeeso baaben am: o wattinat ji'oowo. ngaddanon kam …ďeynguure mon nden …ďe denndaangal""."
  12,94,"Nde setee…ďe …ďen ceerti [yalti Misra]ben ma…ď…ďe maaki: ""miin mi…óo he…ďa balangol Yuusufa, sinno wanaa fii yo on …óaaytinam""."
  12,95,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""min ngoo…óndirii Alla, an ha…óa e majjere maa…óa …ďooyunde nden""."
  12,96,"Nde beltinoowo on arnoo, o werlii [dolokke] on ka yeeso makko, o wonti yi'oowo. O maaki: ""E mi wi'anaano on mi…óo anndi ka Alla ko on nganndaa?"""
  12,97,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""eheyma yo baaba amen, imsinano men junuubi amen. minen men ngoniino woop…ďe""."
  12,98,"O maaki: ""Arma mi imsinano on Joomi am. Ko KaŇčko woni jaafotoo…óo, jurmotoo…óo""."
  12,99,"Nde …ďe naatnoo ka Yuusufa, o tappi ka makko […óoun] maw…ďe makko …ďen …ói…óo, o maaki: ""Naatiree Misra, si Alla muuyii, ko on hoolii…ďe""."
  12,100,"O towniri maw…ďe makko …ďen …ói…óo ka belorki(daŇčki), …ďe naayirani mo cujjugol. O maaki:""eymon baaba'en, ko …óum …óoo woni firo koy…óol am ngol oya tuma, gooŇč…óii Joomi am wa…óii ngol goonga. GooŇč…óii O mo∆ī∆īike e am tuma O yaltinnoo kam ka kaso, O itti on ka ladde, …ďaawo nde seytaane bonnii hakkunde am musi…ó…ďe- baab-gootoo…ďe am …ďen. Pellet, Joomi am ko newanii…óo ko O muuyi kon. Ko KaŇčko woni ganndu…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo""."
  12,101,"Joomi am, gooŇč…óii A wee…óii kam laamu, A anndinii kam kadi firo koy…ói. [Aan] Tak…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, ko Aan woni gi…óo am aduna e laakara. ∆≥ettitam ko mi juul…óo, wa…óitdaa kam e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen."
  12,102,"∆äuum ko jeyaa…óum e kumpite wirnii…óe, mi…óen wahayini …óe e maa…óa. A tawanooka e ma…ď…ďe tuma nde …ďe e…ď…ďunoo fiyaaku ma…ď…ďe on he…ďe pewja."
  12,103,"Ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen, hay si a reer…ói, (…ďe) ngonaani gooŇč…óinoo…ďe."
  12,104,"A …óa…ď…ďiraani …ďe e …óuum njo…ďdi. Nde wonaani si wanaa waaju wonan¬īde winndere nden."
  12,105,"∆äuu…óii e aayeeje ka kammuuli e ka leydi, he…ďee ndewa e majje hara ko …ďe …óuurnii…ďe …óe."
  12,106,"Ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe goos…óintaa Alla, si wonaa hara ko …ďe sirku…ďe."
  12,107,"E …ďe kooli nde hippooje arata …ďe e lepte Alla …óee maa darngal ngal ardira …ďe juhal, hara kam…ďe …ďe tinaani"
  12,108,"Maaku: ""Ko ngo'ol woni laawol am, mi…óo noddira e Alla dow hujja, min e …ďeen jokku…ďe kam. Senayee woodanii Alla! Mi wonaani jeyaa…óo e sirkoo…ďe …ďen."
  12,109,"Men nulaali ado maa si wanaa wor…ďe jeyaa…ďe e yim…ďe ca'e …óen, mi…óen mbahayina e ma…ď…ďe. E …ďee [fennoo…ďe ma] yiilotaako ka leydi, …ďe ndaara ko honno battane …ďeen adinoo…ďe …ďe w'anoo? Pellet ko saare laakara nden …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďen hul…ďe [Alla]. E on haqqiltaa?"
  12,110,"Haa si tawii nulaa…ďe …ďen ta∆īike, (heefer…ďe …ďen) fellita won¬īde kam…ďe …ďe fennaama, ballal amen ngal ara e ma…ď…ďe; min da…ónda on mo min muuyi, lepte amen …óen ruttetaake gaayi e yim…ďe bon…ďe …ďen."
  12,111,"GooŇč…óii wonii e fillayeeje ma…ď…ďe …óin tasakuyye wonan`de joomiraa…ďe haqqillaaji …ďen. Nde wonaani yewtere fekidaande. Ko woni, ko nde gooŇč…óinnde …óen adinoo…óe nde, e fensitunde kala huunde, e peewal e yurmeende wonan¬īde yim…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
